title: End Of Year Review Before Heading Into 2022!
description:
What a fabulous year! We were blessed with two Taylor's Version albums, so many new vault songs, the ATWTMVTVFTV, the short film, and we made so many fun memories on this podcast! Let's take a walk down memory lane and relive some of those fun moments!
And most importantly, happy new year! We are very excited to see what this next year brings for us all, and to find out what magic Blondie is going come up with next!
What did we leave out? What would you like to hear from us next year? There are lots of ways to reach us and we love hearing from you!
